OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'kleptocrat' book High     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FCourt libel case           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A libel claim brought by a post-Soviet 
OL,6, mining giant against a journalist's    
OL,7, book about dirty money and corruption  
OL,8, has been dismissed by a High Court.    
OL,10,FTom Burgis faced potentially huge      
OL,11,Fdamages over his book, Kleptopia.      
OL,13,FBut judge Mr Justice Nicklin stopped   
OL,14,Fthe case after finding the claim       
OL,15,Fagainst the author to be wholly flawed.
OL,17,FMr Burgis' publisher said the case had 
OL,18,Fbeen an attempt to use legal and       
OL,19,Ffinancial firepower to silence public  
OL,20,Finterest journalism.                   
